password: #string38 random - The password for the configured agent's communication and storage
initial_messages: ?list_command optional - A list of commands to run before the first C2 loop
periodic_messages: ?list_command optional - A list of commands to run before each subsequent C2 loop
callback_url: ?string required - The callback URL for the C2 server
user_agent: ?string required - The user-agent string for the HTTP(S) communications
